  "summary": "Pillow has an out-of-bounds write when loading PSD images",
  "details": "Pillow is a Python imaging library. From 10.3.0 to before 12.1.1, an out-of-bounds write may be triggered when loading a specially crafted PSD image. This vulnerability is fixed in 12.1.1.",
